#WSL# 

open powershell as administrator and type wsl --install 
once thats install reboot


##Docker Installation##

https://docs.docker.com/desktop/setup/install/windows-install/

download the docker desktop file from the above link

open the docker desktop installed.exe and install docker 

then open the terminal in the docker desktop (bottom right)

and then 
paste this command 

docker run -p 6080:80 --security-opt seccomp=unconfined --shm-size=512m tiryoh/ros2-desktop-vnc:humble

thats it , once the container starts running  , 

open your browser and then type in http://127.0.0.1:6080/

enjoy
